data.description: Welcome to your dream home, a stunning and completely updated 3-bed, 2 -bath haven of modern luxury.  Selling now, a modern and beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that defines contemporary luxury. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the sleek design, flooded with natural light, and open-concept living spaces that create an inviting atmosphere. The chef's kitchen boasts top-of-the-line appliances and a spacious kitchen, perfect for entertaining. The master suite is a true retreat with an en-suite bathroom with an updated stand up shower , while two additional bedrooms provide versatile space for family or guests. The backyard offers an oasis of serenity, complete with a huge yard for outdoor enjoyment. This meticulously designed home combines form and function, offering the epitome of modern living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary property your own.
